My vegetarian version was really delicious. The key is seasoning it enough. Taste it to make sure there is enough salt. I used 4 eggs and 1 cup ricotta. Cheeses were feta and mozarella. Veggies were sund dried tomatoes, mushrooms and garlic. Topped it with kalamata olive halves, pine nuts, parmesan, and a drizzle of olive oil. Fresh herbs added alot of flavor.

