Really liked this pie! I used some shredded monterey jack cheese and some mozzarella that I had on hand and it was good. Used crushed garlic in a jar and used angel hair instead of spaghetti. Also used one yolk and 8 whites instead of 8 whole eggs. Assembled pie in the afternoon and refrigerated for 3 or so hours, then baked at dinner time. I think I would spray a pie plate and bake it in that instead of the skillet next time. It took me days to clean the pan. I will make it again.

